      "html": "<style data-kid=\"0\">\n@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Public+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');\n@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont/tabler-icons.min.css');\n</style>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Public Sans', sans-serif; color: #36454F; background-color: #FAF0E6; min-width: 375px;\" data-kid=\"1\">\n\n  <header style=\"background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid #F2E8EF; height: 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0 16px;\" data-kid=\"2\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;\" data-kid=\"3\">\n      <div style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; background: #6B3558; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"4\">\n        <i class=\"ti ti-tooth\" style=\"color: white; font-size: 15px;\" data-kid=\"5\"></i>\n      </div>\n      <span style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; color: #36454F;\" data-kid=\"6\">Dr. Tomte</span>\n    </div>\n    <button style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;\" data-kid=\"7\">\n      <i class=\"ti ti-menu-2\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #36454F;\" data-kid=\"8\"></i>\n    </button>\n  </header>\n\n  <section style=\"background: #FAF0E6; padding: 44px 20px 36px; text-align: center;\" data-kid=\"9\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: #6B3558; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 10px;\" data-kid=\"10\">Home · Leistungen</p>\n    <h1 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 34px; font-weight: 700; color: #36454F; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 12px;\" data-kid=\"11\">Unsere Leistungen</h1>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.65; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;\" data-kid=\"12\">Von Vorsorge bis ästhetische Zahnheilkunde</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section style=\"background: #F2E8EF; padding: 28px 20px;\" data-kid=\"13\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 220px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.2); border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(107,53,88,0.35); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 18px;\" data-kid=\"14\">\n      <i class=\"ti ti-mood-kid\" style=\"font-size: 60px; color: #6B3558; margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-kid=\"15\"></i>\n      <span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 500;\" data-kid=\"16\">[Foto: Kind beim Zahnarzt — glücklich]</span>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap;\" data-kid=\"17\">\n      <span style=\"background: #6B3558; color: white; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 13px; border-radius: 20px;\" data-kid=\"18\">⭐ Schwerpunkt Nr. 1</span>\n      <span style=\"background: rgba(107,53,88,0.12); color: #6B3558; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 4px 13px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(107,53,88,0.3);\" data-kid=\"19\">Kinderecke vorhanden</span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 10px;\" data-kid=\"20\">Kinderzahnheilkunde</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.72; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 18px;\" data-kid=\"21\">Die Zahngesundheit von Kindern liegt uns besonders am Herzen. In unserer liebevoll gestalteten Praxis mit eigener Kinderecke behandeln wir kleine Patienten mit Geduld, Einfühlungsvermögen und kindgerechter Kommunikation.</p>\n    <button style=\"width: 100%; background: #6B3558; color: white; border: none; padding: 14px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Public Sans', sans-serif; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;\" data-kid=\"22\">\n      <i class=\"ti ti-calendar\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-kid=\"23\"></i>Kinderzahnarzt-Termin buchen\n    </button>\n  </section>\n\n  <section style=\"background: white; padding: 28px 20px;\" data-kid=\"24\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px;\" data-kid=\"25\">\n      <div style=\"width: 4px; height: 24px; background: #6B3558; border-radius: 4px;\" data-kid=\"26\"></div>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"27\">Prävention</h2>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;\" data-kid=\"28\">\n      <div style=\"background: #FAF0E6; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(107,53,88,0.15);\" data-kid=\"29\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.12); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"30\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-shield-check\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"31\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"32\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"33\">Individualprophylaxe</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"34\">Professionelle Zahnreinigung & persönliche Vorsorge für Erwachsene.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"35\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"background: #FAF0E6; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(107,53,88,0.15);\" data-kid=\"36\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.12); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"37\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-heart\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"38\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"39\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"40\">Seniorenzahnmedizin</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"41\">Schonende und altersgerechte zahnmedizinische Versorgung.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"42\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section style=\"background: #FAF0E6; padding: 28px 20px;\" data-kid=\"43\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px;\" data-kid=\"44\">\n      <div style=\"width: 4px; height: 24px; background: #6B3558; border-radius: 4px;\" data-kid=\"45\"></div>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"46\">Zahnerhaltung</h2>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;\" data-kid=\"47\">\n      <div style=\"background: white; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid #F2E8EF;\" data-kid=\"48\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.1); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"49\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-tool\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"50\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"51\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"52\">Hochwertige Füllungen</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"53\">Kunststofffüllungen & Keramikinlays in natürlicher Optik.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"54\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"background: white; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid #F2E8EF;\" data-kid=\"55\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.1); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"56\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-circle-x\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"57\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"58\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"59\">Amalgamentfernung</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"60\">Schonende Entfernung und Sanierung alter Amalgamfüllungen.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"61\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"background: white; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid #F2E8EF;\" data-kid=\"62\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.1); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"63\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-activity\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"64\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"65\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"66\">Wurzelbehandlung / Endodontie</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"67\">Schonende Behandlung zur Rettung des natürlichen Zahns.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"68\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"background: white; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid #F2E8EF;\" data-kid=\"69\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.1); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"70\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-chart-line\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"71\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"72\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"73\">Parodontosebehandlung</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"74\">Gezielte Therapie bei Zahnfleischerkrankungen.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"75\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section style=\"background: white; padding: 28px 20px;\" data-kid=\"76\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px;\" data-kid=\"77\">\n      <div style=\"width: 4px; height: 24px; background: #6B3558; border-radius: 4px;\" data-kid=\"78\"></div>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"79\">Prothetik</h2>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;\" data-kid=\"80\">\n      <div style=\"background: #FAF0E6; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(107,53,88,0.15);\" data-kid=\"81\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.12); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"82\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-crown\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"83\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"84\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"85\">Kronen & Brücken</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"86\">Hochwertige festsitzende Versorgung für dauerhaften Halt.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"87\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"background: #FAF0E6; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(107,53,88,0.15);\" data-kid=\"88\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.12); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"89\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-bolt\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"90\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"91\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"92\">Implantatprothetik</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"93\">Zuverlässige Implantatlösungen für fehlende Zähne.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"94\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"background: #FAF0E6; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(107,53,88,0.15);\" data-kid=\"95\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.12); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"96\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-diamond\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"97\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"98\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"99\">Vollkeramik / Zirkonoxid</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"100\">Ästhetische, metallfreie Restaurationen in höchster Qualität.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"101\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section style=\"background: #FAF0E6; padding: 28px 20px;\" data-kid=\"102\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px;\" data-kid=\"103\">\n      <div style=\"width: 4px; height: 24px; background: #6B3558; border-radius: 4px;\" data-kid=\"104\"></div>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"105\">Weitere Leistungen</h2>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;\" data-kid=\"106\">\n      <div style=\"background: white; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid #F2E8EF;\" data-kid=\"107\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.1); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"108\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-adjustments\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"109\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"110\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"111\">Knirscher- & Schnarchschiene</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"112\">Individuelle Schienen gegen Bruxismus und Schnarchen.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"113\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"background: white; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid #F2E8EF;\" data-kid=\"114\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.1); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"115\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-wind\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"116\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"117\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"118\">Behandlung von Mundgeruch</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"119\">Ursachenforschung und nachhaltige Therapie.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"120\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"background: white; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; border: 1px solid #F2E8EF;\" data-kid=\"121\">\n        <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(107,53,88,0.1); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"122\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-sun\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #6B3558;\" data-kid=\"123\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"124\">\n          <h3 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #36454F; margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"125\">Bleaching</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #36454F; opacity: 0.62; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"126\">Professionelle Zahnaufhellung für ein strahlendes Lächeln.</p>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #6B3558; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"127\">Mehr →</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section style=\"background: #36454F; padding: 44px 20px; text-align: center;\" data-kid=\"128\">\n    <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin: 0 0 8px;\" data-kid=\"129\">Keine Sorge bei Kosten</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.62); margin: 0 0 28px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic;\" data-kid=\"130\">\"Was wir vorhaben, erläutern wir Ihnen fair und verständlich.\"</p>\n    <button style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 295px; background: #6B3558; color: white; border: none; padding: 15px 24px; border-radius: 40px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; font-family: 'Public Sans', sans-serif;\" data-kid=\"131\">\n      <i class=\"ti ti-calendar\" data-kid=\"132\"></i>Termin vereinbaren\n    </button>\n  </section>\n\n  <footer style=\"background: #2A1E28; padding: 32px 20px 24px;\" data-kid=\"133\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 18px;\" data-kid=\"134\">\n      <div style=\"width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; background: #6B3558; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"135\">\n        <i class=\"ti ti-tooth\" style=\"color: white; font-size: 14px;\" data-kid=\"136\"></i>\n      </div>\n      <span style=\"font-family: 'Lora', serif; color: white; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\" data-kid=\"137\">Zahnarztpraxis Dr. Tomte</span>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 20px;\" data-kid=\"138\">Volpinistraße 19<br data-kid=\"139\">80638 München – Nymphenburg</p>\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;\" data-kid=\"140\">\n      <div data-kid=\"141\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin: 0 0 8px;\" data-kid=\"142\">Kontakt</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin: 0 0 4px;\" data-kid=\"143\">089 / 178 33 50</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"144\">praxis@zahnarztpraxis-tomte.de</p>\n      </div>\n      <div data-kid=\"145\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin: 0 0 8px;\" data-kid=\"146\">Leistungen</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"147\">Kinderzahnheilkunde</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"148\">Prophylaxe</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin: 0 0 3px;\" data-kid=\"149\">Prothetik</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"150\">Bleaching</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 16px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\" data-kid=\"151\">\n      <p style=\"font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.32); margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"152\">© Dr. Tomte 2012–2025</p>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 14px; font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.32);\" data-kid=\"153\">\n        <span data-kid=\"154\">Datenschutz</span><span data-kid=\"155\">Impressum</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n\n  <div style=\"background: white; border-top: 1.5px solid #F2E8EF; padding: 12px 16px; display: flex; gap: 12px;\" data-kid=\"156\">\n    <button style=\"flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 7px; padding: 13px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1.5px solid #6B3558; background: none; color: #6B3558; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Public Sans', sans-serif;\" data-kid=\"157\">\n      <i class=\"ti ti-phone\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-kid=\"158\"></i><span data-kid=\"159\">Anrufen</span>\n    </button>\n    <button style=\"flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 7px; padding: 13px; border-radius: 12px; border: none; background: #6B3558; color: white; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Public Sans', sans-serif;\" data-kid=\"160\">\n      <i class=\"ti ti-calendar\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-kid=\"161\"></i><span data-kid=\"162\">Termin</span>\n    </button>\n  </div>\n</div>",
